reviewText: Lovely and beautiful  and brite colosr in this video wish it was longer

Loved this parade at Disneyland, we were there for one of the last performances. Bought the VHS tape at Disneyland that day, still have it, it still works too. Such a special memory. I do wish they would come out with it on DVD.

Awesome video of the Lion King Parade, no longer at Disneyland, this was and is my absolute favorite parade, having the video is the next best thing to being there, as it brings back those wonderful memories.
